{
  "texts": [
    "For screened patients, the baseline time is the screening date minus 5 years.",
    "The 5-year period was selected because events that happened prior to the 5-year cut-off were considered not to have a substantial effect on screening decisions.",
    "For patients who were never screened, the baseline time is the \"expected screening date\" (calculated as the time from their first visit plus the average time to screening from the first visit for screened patients) minus 5 years.",
    "This process is further described in the Description of the dataset used for analysis subsection.",
    "Patient phenotyping using EHR dataWe extracted information from the EHR in Epic (Epic Systems Corporation, Verona WI) on all patients in the MUSC Health network aged 40 + and their respective clinical notes, diagnoses, and procedural data spanning 2012 through 2022."
  ]
}